(x_1,y_1)
(X,Y)
(x-x_0)^2+(y-y_0)^2=r^2
(X-x_0)^2+(Y-y_0)^2=r^2
(X-x_1)^2+(Y-y_1)^2=L^2
(x-h)^2+(y-k)^2=r^2
(r\cos\theta+h,r\sin\theta+k)
S(p,q)
\theta
(r\cos\theta+h-p)^2+(r\sin\theta+k-q)=L^2
\implies 2r(h-p)\cos\theta+2r(k-q)\sin\theta=L^2-r^2-(h-p)^2-(k-q)^2
-\sqrt{c^2+d^2}\le c\cos A+d\sin A\le \sqrt{c^2+d^2}
c\cos A+d\sin A
c=R\cos B,d=R\sin B
R\ge0
c^2+d^2=R^2\implies R=\sqrt{c^2+d^2}
\tan B=\frac dc
c\cos A+d\sin A=\sqrt{c^2+d^2}\cos(A-B)
-1\le\cos(A-B)\le1, -\sqrt{c^2+d^2}\le\sqrt{c^2+d^2}\cos(A-B)\le \sqrt{c^2+d^2}
\implies -\sqrt{c^2+d^2}\le \cos A+d\sin A\le \sqrt{c^2+d^2}
